      606,
      1217
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "C. $(x-2)^2 + (y-1)^2 + z^2 = 8$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      863,
      1173,
      1278,
      1217
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "D. $(x-2)^2 + (y-1)^2 + z^2 = 64$."
