    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\nR = AB = \\sqrt{(0-2)^2 + (1-1)^2 + (2-0)^2} = \\sqrt{(-2)^2 + 0^2 + 2^2} = \\sqrt{4+0+4} = \\sqrt{8}.\n$$"
